attributes.patientInstruction:
Preparations:
- Please remember if you are more than 15 minutes late for your appointment you may be rescheduled.  If you have relevant prior imaging please obtain copies and bring them with you to your appointment.  Should you have any questions regarding the reason why this exam has been ordered please refer to the ordering provider.  Kindly give at least one day’s notice if you are unable to make your appointment by calling 509-434-7331 for CT or 509-434-7358 for MRI. You may also cancel at the time of your reminder call.
- Check in is located on the second floor of the main hospital building.  Proceed to the second floor, exit to the right and turn left down the hall following the signage to the Diagnostic Imaging department patient check-in.
- Please arrive 15 mins early
- Do not eat anything for four (4) hours prior to the exam
- Two hours before your scheduled appointment, drink 2 cups of water (16
oz.). You may take any necessary medications.
